{"tid":2437914,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"RED VELVET YERI 拍戲中，成員與 TWICE 娜璉送上應援","createTime":"2021-03-08T07:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:20:33.000Z","uid":222155,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29ec57892053628a274c28cab46b4e12ea0f0bd1","tid":2437914,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet YERI 拍攝戲劇出道作，成員與 TWICE <span class=\"red\">娜璉</span>為她應援加油。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-en-koreaportal-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/images.en.koreaportal.com/data/images/full/43384/red-velvets-yeri-and-twices-nayeon-on-yeris-room.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-en-koreaportal-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fimages.en.koreaportal.com%2Fdata%2Fimages%2Ffull%2F43384%2Fred-velvets-yeri-and-twices-nayeon-on-yeris-room.png&h=525f6d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3日，YERI 在自己的 IG 上分享了兩則貼文，是她同團成員與 TWICE 娜璉為了她正在拍攝戲劇出道作 tvN《Drama Stage》獨幕劇《Mint Condition》送來的應援車照片，YERI 在劇中飾演護理師 Chae Ri 一角。<br />\n<br />\nYERI 在分享 Red Velvet 成員送上的應援車認證照 (如下圖) 說：「謝謝我的團員們，YERI 可靠的朋友們。我愛你。」照片中橫幅寫著：「謝謝《Mint Condition》工作人員辛勞地工作！」，另一個上面寫道：「工作人員們，您們做得很好！Kim Ye Rim (YERI 本名)，您也做得很好。」車上則是標註「我們正在為工作人員和演員加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNz07oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNz07oL.png&h=77c5371f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在 TWICE <span class=\"red\">娜璉</span>認證照貼文中，YERI 寫著：「我很不好意思，但我會炫耀一下。娜璉，謝謝。我永遠愛你。」<span class=\"red\">娜璉送上的應援車橫幅寫著：「請照顧好 Chae Ri，直到最後，《Mint Condition》加油！！」</span>另一個寫上：「謝謝您一起參與 YERI 的第一部作品《Mint Condition》！天氣很冷，請保持力量到最後！加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kpopn.com/2021/03/06/red-velvet-yeri-thanks-members-and-twice-nayeon-support\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2F2021%2F03%2F06%2Fred-velvet-yeri-thanks-members-and-twice-nayeon-support&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=2543633f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kpopn.com/2021/03/06/red-velvet-yeri-thanks-members-and-twice-nayeon-support</a>"},{"pid":"0173d1145258b36bd9a39df460bf222b4d719b68","tid":2437914,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"我璉真係心地又好，朋友又多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd997135a4d196c7f3ae5db0a7602bc493a22193","tid":2437914,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"IRENE恰YERI<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個恰娜璉？😮"},{"pid":"c9c7130e24bb614b54b2d0ca1bba0fdee64cfba3","tid":2437914,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bd997135a4d196c7f3ae5db0a7602bc493a22193","tid":2437914,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"IRENE恰YERI<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個恰娜璉？😮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"多腎Bitch"},{"pid":"ef144c5f94dd78cc049d979ea273f566a6b0542d","tid":2437914,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c9c7130e24bb614b54b2d0ca1bba0fdee64cfba3","tid":2437914,"uid":222155,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bd997135a4d196c7f3ae5db0a7602bc493a22193","tid":2437914,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"IRENE恰YERI<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個恰娜璉？😮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"多腎Bitch"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\n<br />\n娜璉都係比IRENE恰<br />\n<br />\n因為IRENE閪到80任何人🤙🏼"},{"pid":"9cf66bcdb73488603513b9d779c726247878fcf9","tid":2437914,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"自己隊都無人送要隔離隊既人送<br />\nRV解散啦"},{"pid":"ae23682e98ac57e882354f1039cf04d2102b422b","tid":2437914,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9cf66bcdb73488603513b9d779c726247878fcf9","tid":2437914,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislik